    <section ids="high-availability-for-dhcp config-dhcp-ha" names="high-availability\ for\ dhcp config-dhcp-ha">
        <title>High-availability for DHCP</title>
        <paragraph>This section describes how to use the agent management (alias agent) and
            scheduler (alias agent_scheduler) extensions for DHCP agents
            scalability and HA.</paragraph>
        <note>
            <paragraph>Use the <literal_strong classes="command">openstack extension list</literal_strong> command to check if these
                extensions are enabled. Check <literal>agent</literal> and <literal>agent_scheduler</literal>
                are included in the output.</paragraph>
